The idea I used is simple, i used z and j two pointers where z is to keep track of zeroes and j for swapping any non-zero element with the zeroes.
* if nums[z] = 0 and nums[j] is not 0 then we swap these two elements and increment accordingly.
* if nums[z] is not 0 then we just increment z so that we get to some index where the element is 0.
* otherwise we increment only j as in this case nums[z] will contain 0, with j we try to find the next non-zero number.

