![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/d53c6a9e-1e14-404f-9e76-8c28dc7b6bd9_1655193315.6677568.png)

So, length of word1 = 3, length of word2 = 3, lcs=2
answer = 3+3-2*2 = 2


**Approach-2:** We direct calculate minimum no. of steps to make both the strings same using dp

**TC: O(MxN), SC: O(MxN)**

