# Intuition
``` markdown []
* Find the longest common sequence (lcs) between word1 & word2.
* To make the words same, remove all characters other than lcs. 
* let n be word1 length & m be word2 length.
* Result will be (n - lcs) + (m - lcs) = n + m - 2 * lcs
