## Recursive Approach

### Complexity
-  TC (Time Complexity): The time complexity is O(2^(m+n)), making this approach inefficient for larger input sizes. 
- SC (Space Complexity): In the worst case, where there are no common characters between the strings, the recursion depth can be as high as m + n. Hence, the space complexity is O(m + n) for the recursive implementation.

